**Who it's for:**

Pro se litigants • Clinics • Educators • Reform-minded practitioners

**What it does:**

✅ Compute Y★ (rule-pure outcome)

✅ Log discretion (Y ≠ Y★)

✅ Build procedural memory

✅ Teach justice as reproducible code

